Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.00,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,== 字幕制作：泰坦巨人 ==
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.66,0:00:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.20,0:00:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.62,0:00:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都叫我小慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.69,0:00:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我已经很知足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.88,0:01:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟建斌一起生活了七年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三个月前我丢了工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.64,0:03:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都在这儿来回坐着地铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.02,0:03:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里省钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这种感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随遇而安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.91,0:03:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有干扰，自由自在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有他们陪着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，又是我，王要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.91,0:03:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想问问你\N有没有类似红颜色的裙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.87,0:03:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红色的，为什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.09,0:03:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱不是第一次见面嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.04,0:03:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕认差了，啊，对对对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.43,0:03:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红颜色比较好认呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红花的裙子行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.40,0:03:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好，那咱就不见不散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.22,0:03:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能听见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她又站在我的身后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该转过身去冲她微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大大方方的问一句你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.98,0:03:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一年来我有好多次这样的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.21,0:03:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我就是没有勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱情成了我生活中\N唯一靠得住的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.11,0:04:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是没有勇气\N告诉小慧事实和真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道我怕什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.27,0:04:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失败让我在她面前没了自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.33,0:04:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我特别想抱着她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.06,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.50,0:04:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我十九岁生日那天\N我一定要向她说声你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三十四岁都过了一个半月了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.24,0:04:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是渴望能碰到一份\N属于自己的真感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.56,0:04:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉出人来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屋里烧了人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.13,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这火着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.50,0:05:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.00,0:05:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样你不就记住我了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是建斌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.79,0:05:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大学毕业和小慧一起来到北京\N已经7年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是1993年11月20号，下午6点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.52,0:06:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们，刘建斌和陈小慧来到北京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.55,0:06:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.09,0:06:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年了我们还在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.32,0:06:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依然相爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还差四十一天我就二十八岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前我就想弄明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一段感情真的能熬到天荒地老吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，我不想再骗你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有三个月没有工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没敢告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.95,0:07:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是说我不自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.58,0:07:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直挺担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水龙头还在漏水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，我想跟你说件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.55,0:08:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房东来要房租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.96,0:08:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没钱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现场报导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.19,0:08:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天傍晚18点钟左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里发生了一起煤气爆炸事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前医护人员\N已经赶到现场进行抢救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.37,0:08:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据初步统计，目前现场四人轻伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一人重伤，无人死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关于爆炸原因\N警方正在进行有关调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请继续关注我台的报导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，我不想再骗你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.00,0:09:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有三个月没有工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没敢告诉你？是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.68,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房钱咱们俩先一人一半吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说好了下半年\N还要去新马泰呢吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.69,0:09:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，刚才想跟我说什么来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.66,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥，没，没什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么老说半截话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.41,0:09:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才一打岔我给忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀，明天赶紧把钱给房东吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.95,0:09:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不然回家连大声说话都不敢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，你看这儿有这么一句话：
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.76,0:09:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有的人在一段时间里\N可以欺骗所有的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.25,0:09:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而有的人用一生来欺骗一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这句话说的怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.56,0:10:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.83,0:11:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢？这个事儿是不是怨我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地儿是我约的，时间是我定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还让人换了一条红花裙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我要认了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就怕所有的事儿全归到我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我扛的住吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人就是为了等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.93,0:11:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好几宿没睡好觉了\N掉了好几斤肉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说咱哥们儿哪碰过这么大事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我这事做的是不是挺不道德的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.21,0:11:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，我就问问你\N你觉得那姑娘长的靠谱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有她照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.83,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幼儿园教音乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长得还算可以吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.97,0:12:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说我这么做是不是不太道德呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都已经做出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.89,0:12:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看看，可以的话就可以开印了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，着什么急呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有事儿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歇会儿，喝杯咖啡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.53,0:12:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，没时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一杯咖啡需要多少时间呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.48,0:12:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是逃课，出来溜溜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.30,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没那闲心，我还有好多安排呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝咖啡是个过程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.36,0:13:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这样是不会体会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，喝一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这店是你自己开的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.83,0:13:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该说是为自己开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.06,0:13:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算是我的人生理想之一吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.71,0:13:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你人生梦想就这么小呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.88,0:13:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.97,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都瘦了，你看你看你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.03,0:13:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都瘦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.66,0:13:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你们这样上班族的太辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.66,0:13:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁没吃早饭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别骗我举一下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就举一下手嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没吃早饭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你的脸色都看的出来呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为有了我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,俗话说的好：人是铁，饭是钢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.29,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是“人是铁营养食品公司”推出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.04,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专为城市人，成功人士而设计的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满足了不同层次，不同文化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.99,0:14:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不同性别，不同职位人的需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.65,0:14:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们这么说吧，要想轻松每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭前一支人是铁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.43,0:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你找谁呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，那个救小孩\N被烧伤的老师住在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.37,0:15:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗷，她在院儿里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.99,0:15:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彬彬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.71,0:15:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彬彬，你在哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.37,0:15:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.90,0:15:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉阿姨你长大了想干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想在公共汽车上卖票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.63,0:15:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在都是无人售票
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经下岗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.32,0:15:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正还有公共汽车呢\N你说对不对呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.34,0:15:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杨杨，你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.82,0:15:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么也不告诉你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.07,0:16:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我有，就是不告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.83,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想学外星人说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.54,0:16:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，那个人睡着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.32,0:16:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.98,0:16:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那咱们得小点声，别把他吵醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们回病房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.45,0:16:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨给你们讲故事去好不好呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么这么大劲儿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你女孩，还是走旁边走的路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.44,0:17:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忘了上次\N看一棵树是什么时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.49,0:19:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么想起到这儿来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.80,0:19:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发工资了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.97,0:19:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房钱都快交不起了\N还来这么贵的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.87,0:19:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直都想吃这的牛排吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.14,0:19:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就想带你来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.49,0:19:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N一顿饭就想让你跟我乱搞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.45,0:19:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀，讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.55,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.24,0:20:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你哪位呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，我还是喜欢你不化妆的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你还是化妆比较好看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.37,0:21:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显得成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底笑什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.93,0:22:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天老板通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.39,0:22:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要送我去法国培训考察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.35,0:22:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到我和小慧\N会开始一种口是心非的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.70,0:23:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.39,0:23:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么可看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.63,0:23:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，真要去法国这么久啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.95,0:23:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才吃饭的时候\N你不是去洗手间了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.43,0:23:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有个叫老虎的打你的手机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.09,0:23:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.74,0:24:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都叫我小慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.14,0:24:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我已经很知足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.29,0:24:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能跟建斌在一起生活了七年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.39,0:24:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为自己会是一个贤妻良母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.79,0:24:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.51,0:24:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得咱们俩是不是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.04,0:24:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老有一种乐极生悲的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.91,0:24:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得人一辈子的爱就那么多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.07,0:24:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像花钱似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.86,0:24:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人匀着使能使一辈子\N平平淡淡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.34,0:24:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们俩好像有点儿太挥霍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.79,0:25:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像一下子就花完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.23,0:25:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀，你就会胡思乱想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.10,0:25:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你出道题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.28,0:25:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.75,0:25:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个甘蔗，一头是甜的\N一头是苦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.28,0:25:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃哪头？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.69,0:25:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先吃苦的，把甜的留在最后吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:23.39,0:25:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就说明你是一个悲观主义者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.79,0:25:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对前途没什么信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.52,0:25:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.40,0:25:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然吃甜的那头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.30,0:25:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我是甜的是苦的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.32,0:25:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.52,0:25:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道从什么时候起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.43,0:25:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种感觉不再有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.88,0:26:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都已经习惯了眼前这种生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.32,0:26:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我已经27岁的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.32,0:26:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始怀疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.31,0:26:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会再有砰然心动的感觉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:10.00,0:27:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟！都瘦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.40,0:27:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家都瘦啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.13,0:27:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们都市人实在太辛苦啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.90,0:27:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还没吃早饭呢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.00,0:27:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没吃早饭的请举手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.94,0:27:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是人是铁公司赠品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.09,0:27:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎试用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.76,0:27:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用赠了，我买10支
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:40.71,0:28:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N我要真的上去就一切都毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.83,0:28:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从小到大我就是这么一种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.39,0:28:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生了什么事\N都会在我自己身上找原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.94,0:28:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕是她真背叛了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:58.11,0:29:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也肯定是我这儿出了什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.52,0:29:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天晚上给你打电话\N没给你惹麻烦吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.17,0:29:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.55,0:29:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:37.58,0:29:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别老跟着我好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.93,0:29:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你是谁呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.14,0:29:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我一天到晚没？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.26,0:29:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.08,0:30:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作人有一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.32,0:30:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是对自己的情感诚实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.36,0:30:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.18,0:30:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们握一下手，先从朋友做起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.52,0:30:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她看我干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.96,0:30:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他没睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.81,0:30:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像一堵墙躺在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:09.93,0:31:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建斌，你睡了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:16.58,0:31:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得咱们在学校第一次\N出去是什么时候吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.36,0:31:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她问这个干什么？嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:30.14,0:31:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是七月份吧，挺热的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.92,0:31:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他全忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.85,0:31:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也记不清了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.21,0:31:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像是个星期六
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:48.15,0:31:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们俩一起走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:50.13,0:31:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没说一句话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.30,0:31:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到把你那双破鞋的鞋跟\N给走掉咱们才回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.94,0:32:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼，这事你怎么记那么清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.21,0:32:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记得清楚的事还多着呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.34,0:32:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一晃就是七年多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.23,0:32:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回顾就是为了告别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.41,0:32:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为过去伤感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:20.49,0:32:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来是要向我摊牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:22.57,0:32:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掀开人生新的一页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:27.01,0:32:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,气人，这样的尝试\N我曾经做过无数次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.55,0:32:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是想回忆过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:35.10,0:32:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看现在真是不堪入目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.75,0:32:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么到最后\N他总是撅着个屁股对着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.09,0:33:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不问她呢，我没这么傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.65,0:33:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她为什么一点儿都不知道争取呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.44,0:33:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道他就知道放弃、躲避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.64,0:33:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在保持尊严的唯一办法就是沉默
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.49,0:33:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会让他满意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.92,0:33:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼？对不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.63,0:33:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:24.27,0:33:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.87,0:33:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，你去法国那事怎么样了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.62,0:33:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么也没听你提呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.86,0:33:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正办着呢，快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.60,0:35:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.26,0:35:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.84,0:35:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.18,0:35:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开荒种地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.80,0:35:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.39,0:35:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.80,0:35:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在山里租了一片地种树
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.95,0:35:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:22.24,0:36:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈？你是谁呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.84,0:36:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们认识吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.59,0:37:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候走呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.59,0:37:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在想弄明白，我到底该不该走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:23.84,0:37:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:29.41,0:37:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为自己是一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.74,0:37:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么牵挂都不会有的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.63,0:37:36.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是没想到遇到了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.34,0:37:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们不就只是好朋友嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:03.50,0:38:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.99,0:38:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂？是建斌吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.16,0:38:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不知道该说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.37,0:38:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我是那样强烈的想念她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.51,0:38:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种冲动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:00.76,0:39:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.03,0:39:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要给七年的这段感情一次机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:08.27,0:39:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.68,0:39:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是王要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.31,0:39:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我16岁就没有读书出来赚钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.89,0:39:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从南到北的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.75,0:39:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在想起来就有点儿后怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.65,0:39:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁要你可怜我，谁会可怜我呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:30.50,0:39:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.65,0:39:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人在一起\N谁会保证谁跟谁一辈子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:36.58,0:39:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你也总不能跟一个老女人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.76,0:39:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年之后才告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.73,0:39:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想明白了，你也铁了心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.21,0:39:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你回来我也不要你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.18,0:39:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:51.13,0:39:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找个好人 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.52,0:40:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.13,0:40:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你都跟了我几天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:13.27,0:40:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你多大了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.87,0:40:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,17
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:18.74,0:40:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没戴眼镜儿，你长得怪老的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:23.82,0:40:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个17
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.57,0:40:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老看着我干嘛呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.67,0:40:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就啄磨呀\N为什么在感情世界里受伤害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.04,0:40:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远是我们善良的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.86,0:41:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.76,0:41:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明天下午5点就可以过来取了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.23,0:42:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道为什么我突然有一种预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.19,0:42:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他再也不会来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:42.61,0:42:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建斌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.93,0:42:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像有什么心事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.13,0:42:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.26,0:43:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，其实根本\N就没有去法国那些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:02.86,0:43:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是我为了自己心理平衡瞎编的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:06.28,0:43:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已经有几个月没有工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.20,0:43:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没敢告诉你是怕你为我担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.67,0:43:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不早说呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:26.69,0:43:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应过你要让你幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.09,0:43:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可生活有时候太难了，觉得好累啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:34.75,0:43:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怕你离开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.83,0:44:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那个夜晚我紧张而焦急的等待着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:37.57,0:44:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要那只蟑螂爬到照片那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.45,0:44:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就如实的告诉他一切都是误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:45.31,0:44:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱的就只他一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.38,0:44:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:58.08,0:46:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的名字叫天爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:00.35,0:46:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想约你出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.39,0:46:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天中午的12点，在地铁大望站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:05.72,0:46:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都会在那里等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:07.80,0:46:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你每天那个时候\N都会在那里等车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.25,0:46:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你会来吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:18.48,0:46:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王要，你今天好像情绪不太高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:23.63,0:46:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你谈过恋爱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:25.84,0:46:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我谈过一个，还是上大学的时候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:28.85,0:46:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厨师有大学吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:33.96,0:46:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我大学被开除以后才学的烹饪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.15,0:46:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:41.67,0:46:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿，你接着说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.06,0:46:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来我的事业没成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:46.76,0:46:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她也有了别人，我们俩就分手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:48.64,0:46:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你伤心吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:50.60,0:46:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚分手的时候\N感觉眼前一阵阵发黑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.31,0:46:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是世界末日了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:02.50,0:47:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是后来睁开眼睛看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:04.57,0:47:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周围的一切该怎么样还怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.68,0:47:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得爱情在生活面前\N太微不足道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.51,0:47:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你现在还会想她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:20.28,0:47:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.20,0:47:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就跟看别人演的伤感电影似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:26.90,0:47:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么就成了现在这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:30.74,0:47:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩都不能坦然面对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:34.80,0:47:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我知道他心里在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:37.58,0:47:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我就是没法告诉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:41.84,0:47:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心里其实还是爱他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:47.31,0:47:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:52.33,0:47:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好笑的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:55.02,0:47:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了，别烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:00.61,0:48:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我看我儿子去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:07.75,0:48:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:09.50,0:48:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一出生我就认养了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:11.78,0:48:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:12.99,0:48:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀！哎哟哟，咬阿姨的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:15.68,0:48:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这一走呀，还真有点儿舍不得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:17.69,0:48:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系，你走了以后啊\N我替你照顾它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:20.25,0:48:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后我会常来看它的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:24.31,0:48:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我挺想跟你在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:25.98,0:48:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好玩儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.35,0:48:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他呀\N可能在一起待的时间太长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:31.38,0:48:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，慢慢吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.82,0:48:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖不着急啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:35.51,0:48:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么自己的空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.20,0:48:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有什么自己的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:39.99,0:48:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们的关系特脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.83,0:48:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真怕一瞬间好像什么都变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:48.05,0:48:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得人最难的其实是诚实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:51.44,0:48:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能对自己的感情诚实的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:54.09,0:48:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想没有什么能够一瞬间就改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.52,0:48:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们俩是好朋友吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:00.36,0:49:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说咱们俩的关系过分吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:06.06,0:49:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几天前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:07.37,0:49:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实想过分一下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:09.41,0:49:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在不这么想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:12.96,0:49:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你们俩还是挺相爱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:42.66,0:52:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是喝酒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:52.36,0:52:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:56.96,0:52:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝酒了怎么就不能碰我老婆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:27.79,0:53:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，小慧我不碰你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.69,0:53:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧，小慧，小慧你进来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:41.58,0:53:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了，明天还要上班呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.92,0:54:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越是在这个时候\N千万记住要留门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:05.31,0:54:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,门锁死了机会也就没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:17.34,0:54:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天都亮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:34.26,0:54:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没劲儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:36.44,0:54:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个晚上过去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.39,0:54:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连为什么跑出来我都记不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:41.75,0:54:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的身体我不敢肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:44.05,0:54:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心理已经背叛我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:47.41,0:54:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留人留不住心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.68,0:54:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧我随你去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.69,0:55:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:01.67,0:55:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就不觉得可惜吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:06.12,0:55:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜啊，当然可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:08.97,0:55:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七年了，我们都变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:11.49,0:55:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说白点儿\N就是我们变得不那么单纯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:19.43,0:55:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后半句我的自尊没让我说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:24.48,0:55:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁还能和一个\N事业失败的男人白头偕老呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:25.89,0:56:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没你说的那么胖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:29.00,0:56:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，我一直在偷偷喝减肥茶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:31.55,0:56:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:33.76,0:56:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，脸烧伤了你真的不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:44.57,0:56:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:45.85,0:56:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕什么，能告诉我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:48.38,0:56:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:52.15,0:56:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我拆线的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:54.07,0:56:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要告诉我最亲近的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:58.58,0:56:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:01.46,0:57:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我漂亮吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:07.89,0:57:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己并不漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:10.42,0:57:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以受伤以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:14.16,0:57:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也没觉得失去什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:16.88,0:57:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:18.93,0:57:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你很美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:26.22,0:57:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:27.85,0:57:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有在一个女孩儿面前红过脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:36.17,0:57:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我没什么事儿\N所以提前下班了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:40.58,0:57:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们也好久没在家吃饭了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:58.65,0:57:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建斌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:03.86,0:58:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些话我想跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:10.29,0:58:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱不是说好了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:12.21,0:58:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在感情的事儿上一定要诚实，所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:19.35,0:58:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想告诉你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:31.18,0:58:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她让我心如刀绞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:33.32,0:58:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,7年就像是一大块从我身上切下的肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:38.66,0:58:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不忍心一刀就这么切下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:42.02,0:58:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕还连着这最后的一丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:47.72,0:58:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:59.68,0:59:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:04.51,0:59:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心都凉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:06.65,0:59:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和他好像都在放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:09.85,0:59:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼看我们过去的7年像个小孩一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:12.63,0:59:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在自己面前淹死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:14.94,0:59:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就站在那
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:16.79,0:59:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:34.55,0:59:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还爱我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:35.89,0:59:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:37.23,0:59:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非是你，咬死你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:42.67,0:59:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们在一起那么长时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:44.27,0:59:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你心里就没想过别人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:49.51,0:59:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去年我在上海碰到一个男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:53.45,0:59:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长得特别特别特别的帅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:55.97,0:59:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那后来呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:57.54,0:59:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:59.17,1:00:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:01.22,1:00:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来怎么回事儿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:02.66,1:00:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来我就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:04.71,1:00:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:06.31,1:00:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来我就接着想了想
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:08.19,1:00:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就给你打电话来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:12.74,1:00:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说，咱们俩能好到底吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:17.34,1:00:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咱们不是已经好到底了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:19.77,1:00:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家问你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:23.35,1:00:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有时候咬咬牙坚持住就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:27.32,1:00:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:33.78,1:00:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就比如说你是鱼翅，我是燕窝
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:37.43,1:00:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那总有吃腻的时候吧，吃了一辈子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:39.60,1:00:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在这个时候看见一个大白菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.81,1:00:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就得咬咬牙坚持住
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.11,1:00:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咽口吐沫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:45.36,1:00:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么咬牙呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:56.40,1:00:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还爱我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.41,1:00:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还爱我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:03.37,1:01:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天老板跟我说\N去法国的事儿提前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:08.23,1:01:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有四天就走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:12.13,1:01:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:03.82,1:02:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.17,1:02:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:06.64,1:02:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小老虎的事儿\N我有些东西得交给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:09.58,1:02:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噢，好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:11.53,1:02:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地铁口见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:13.26,1:02:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:33.50,1:02:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.82,1:02:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.26,1:02:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:45.31,1:02:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:48.67,1:02:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:54.52,1:02:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.17,1:03:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多人怎么爱啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:01.24,1:03:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你到底爱不爱我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:06.23,1:03:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们说面对这么可爱的女孩儿\N我能怎么着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:21.77,1:03:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么也在这儿下车了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:23.82,1:03:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有四天我就走了\N送送我老婆不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:28.90,1:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行啊 怎么不行 
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:56.16,1:04:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:57.41,1:04:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:00.06,1:05:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是有嘛，这手都凉成这样啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:05.21,1:05:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好，就算有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:12.41,1:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该高兴点儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:14.07,1:05:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像我每天都特高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:16.66,1:05:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得整天那么高兴挺没根据的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:19.80,1:05:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀，就是心事太重啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:21.43,1:05:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老给自己加压
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:23.25,1:05:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样弄得旁边的人都不轻松
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:27.67,1:05:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:33.14,1:05:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你讲个故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:36.56,1:05:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让我高兴吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:38.29,1:05:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:40.85,1:05:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从前有一个叫玛丽的小女孩儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:44.46,1:05:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她四岁的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:46.32,1:05:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天天使飞到她家里来看她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:49.71,1:05:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使问玛丽：玛丽，你长大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:53.77,1:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么愿望让你帮我实现呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:02.47,1:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽说：
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:03.72,1:06:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想在我二十岁生日的那天\N找到一个男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:08.32,1:06:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫汉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.66,1:06:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有长长的头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:12.13,1:06:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要会弹结他，会唱歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:14.85,1:06:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会生四个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:16.99,1:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都是女孩儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:19.10,1:06:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们会到学校去学芭蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:22.62,1:06:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使听了玛丽的愿望说：
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:25.08,1:06:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧，那我答应你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:27.67,1:06:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就飞走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:43.61,1:07:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么没来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:11.41,1:09:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情真是没法说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:14.57,1:09:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你碰到过这种事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:17.42,1:09:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你的话，你怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:20.30,1:09:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就进去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:22.83,1:09:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不光想杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:24.87,1:09:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我连放火的心都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:29.96,1:09:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在进去又有什么用呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:44.38,1:09:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:45.95,1:09:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一个人等他就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:48.67,1:09:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:49.76,1:09:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你等他回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:51.17,1:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索兴把事儿都谈开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:54.72,1:09:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不是因为你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:00.35,1:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实这只是我们俩之间的事儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:05.82,1:10:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:12.34,1:10:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱里边那个女的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:14.96,1:10:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想让她幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:17.27,1:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是\N她在做对她自己正确的选择
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:21.87,1:10:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:23.89,1:10:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我爱的人找到了她想要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:27.76,1:10:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还能说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:40.33,1:10:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想一个人等他，好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:59.33,1:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:00.58,1:11:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我，别害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:04.32,1:11:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.24,1:11:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:08.00,1:11:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想把故事听完
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:11.23,1:11:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护士来查房了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:14.36,1:11:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天感觉怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:16.06,1:11:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后天你的眼睛就要拆线了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:19.26,1:11:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拆线的时候你在就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:21.59,1:11:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:22.68,1:11:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时别忘通知你的男朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:25.33,1:11:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，他不是我的男朋友\N只是我的普通朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:30.32,1:11:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种天天来看你的普通朋友吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:39.76,1:11:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别听她们瞎说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.82,1:11:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就要拆线了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:47.24,1:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:54.66,1:11:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点儿害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:57.09,1:11:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候我来陪你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:58.82,1:12:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉我你怕什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:01.51,1:12:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不想说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:05.41,1:12:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一件事我一直想告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:10.08,1:12:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管有什么事，先别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:14.11,1:12:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都等到那天再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:18.75,1:12:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，我把那个故事接着给你讲完吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.44,1:12:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽长大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:26.90,1:12:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在她17岁生日的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:29.91,1:12:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她真的遇到了一个叫汉斯的男孩儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:33.75,1:12:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也有长长的头发
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:36.73,1:12:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他不会弹吉他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.85,1:12:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是一个厨子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:44.02,1:12:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们相爱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:46.42,1:12:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的生了四个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:49.04,1:12:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可都是男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:51.05,1:12:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都爱踢足球
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:56.49,1:12:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于有一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:58.16,1:13:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使又飞回来看玛丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:00.68,1:13:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使问：你过得怎么样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:04.84,1:13:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:07.01,1:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么没有给我想要的愿望？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:10.92,1:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使回答：
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:12.81,1:13:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问题是玛丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:14.63,1:13:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也没给我想要的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:18.05,1:13:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:19.94,1:13:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想从我这儿要什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:22.78,1:13:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使说：
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:24.67,1:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要你给我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:26.65,1:13:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:37.59,1:13:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得怎么样啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:40.86,1:13:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:42.42,1:13:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在听吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:10.06,1:14:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们俩特有缘
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:12.07,1:14:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一呢，她是四川人\N我是做川菜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:15.40,1:14:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二呢，她是做营养早餐的\N我是厨子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:19.53,1:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三呢，我爱他，她呢，哈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:34.75,1:14:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:36.42,1:14:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家伙儿是来来往往，忙忙活活
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:39.45,1:14:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 说呢都没说过话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:41.47,1:14:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是在列车上已经都认识了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:43.87,1:14:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我非常高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:45.44,1:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们俩要结婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:46.84,1:14:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿也帮我一起乐呵乐呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:56.50,1:14:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎，我的兄弟呐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:58.10,1:15:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有事 出差了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:01.33,1:15:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他找到工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:03.12,1:15:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是好事  我跟你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:05.17,1:15:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好几个月他没工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:07.19,1:15:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天天在地铁打发时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:09.27,1:15:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真替他担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:11.82,1:15:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:38.57,1:17:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天我也在地铁里穿行着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:42.73,1:17:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:46.03,1:17:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:49.10,1:17:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在地铁里到底是怎么度过的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:12.48,1:18:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天几点钟的飞机呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:15.55,1:18:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:16.93,1:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换洗的内衣内裤\N我给你搁在最里头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:21.85,1:18:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是家里所有的美元
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:23.77,1:18:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放到箱子里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:26.81,1:18:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存折和机票别忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:39.51,1:19:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建斌
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:42.26,1:19:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起死
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:44.18,1:19:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:45.94,1:19:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在后悔还来得及
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:18.83,1:21:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，没事儿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:21.96,1:21:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧，你别吓唬我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:25.74,1:21:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，小慧，哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:29.77,1:21:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧你再闹我跟你急了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:36.48,1:21:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧你怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:39.72,1:21:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说你爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:40.83,1:21:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:42.05,1:21:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快说，你这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:07.97,1:24:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先闭上眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:13.92,1:24:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拆完绷带我就要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:16.96,1:24:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别睁开眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:18.62,1:24:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是你想像的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:32.66,1:24:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还惦记着另外一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:35.16,1:24:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她对你来说很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:57.64,1:24:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:05.86,1:25:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一天我就知道你不是王要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:10.09,1:25:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，可是那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:14.31,1:25:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我身边比任何时候都需要有人陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:17.38,1:25:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你心里还有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:21.03,1:25:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还惦记着另外一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:23.55,1:25:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她对你来说很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:28.09,1:25:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉我你怕什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:32.48,1:25:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最害怕的是我不会哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:16.23,1:26:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是1993年11月20号，下午6点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:19.81,1:26:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们 刘建斌和陈小慧来到北京了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:24.96,1:26:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小慧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:27.59,1:26:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:38.50,1:26:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
 